    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Ribbeſchana no to\nKerubimu Spahrneim tappe\ndſirdeta lihds tam ahrejam Pa-\ngalmam/ tã patt kã ta Wiſſu-\nwarrena Deewa Balsi/ kad tas\nrunna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad Wiſſch tam Wihr-\nram/ kas ar Andekli bija ap-\ngehrbts/ bij pawehlejs/ un faz-\nzijs: Nem Ugguni ſtarp teem\nSkrittekeem ſtarp teem Keru-\nbim/ tad gabje wiſſch eektchã/\nun peestahje pee weena Skritteta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad isſteepe weens Kerubs\nfawu Rohku ſtarp teem Keru-\nbim pee ta Ugguns/ kas ſtarp\nteem Kerubim bija/ un nehme/\nnn dewe to tam Wihram Roh-\nkã/ kas ar Andekli apgehrbts bi-\nja/ tas nehme to/ un tsgahje\nnhra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tur parahdijahs ſtarp\nteem Kerubim/ kas lihdsi bija\nweenai Zilweſtu Rohkai appakſch\nwinnu Spahrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad redſeju Es/ un raug-\ngi/ tſchetri Skritteki bija pee\nteem Kerubim/pee ikkatra Keru-\nba weens Skrittelis/ un tee\nSkritteki bija ta patt ka tas Sil-\nluns weena Turkõſta Akminra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un teem tſchetreem bija ſchee ſtahweja/ nn kad tee zeh-\nweenada Lihtsiba/ itt ka buhtu labs/ tad ir ſchee zehlabs/ jo\nweena Skrittelis ohtra Widdu\nweens dſihws Gars bija eelſch\nteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad * tee gabje/tad gabje\n(ſchee) pa winnu tſchetreem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſa wiſſau Meefa/\nun winnu Muggure/ un winnu\nRohkas/ un winnu Spahrni\nlihds ar teem Skrittekeem bija\npilli Azzu wiſeapkabrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ikweens no teem Skrit-\ntekteem tappe preeſch mannahm\nAutim nofankts Galgals.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ikweenam bij tſchetri\nWaigi/ tas pirmais Waigs bi-\nja weena Keruba Waigs/ un tas\nohtrajs Waigs bija weena Zil-\nweka Waigs/ un tas trefchajs\nWaigs bija weena Lauwa\nWaigs/ un tas zettortajs Waigs\nbija weena Ehrqka Waigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Kerubim zeblahs.\nTas bija tas patã Swehrs/ ko\nes biju redſejs pee tahã Uppes\nRebar.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tee Kerubim gab-\nje/ tad gabje tee Skritteki ſah-\nnis winneem/ un kad tee Keru-\nbim fawus Spahrnus pazehle/\nno Semmes us augſchu zelda-\nmees/ tad ir tee Skritteki no\nwinnu Sahneem ne lohzijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tee ſtahweja/ tad ir\nſchee ſtahweja/ un kad tee zeh-\nlabs/ tad ir ſchee zehlabs/ jo\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad gabje ta KUNGA\nGohdiba no ta Namma Sleek-\nHb 3\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
